Restaurant.Name: Zozolli's Pizzaria
Restaurant.Description: Zozolli's Pizzeria is a popular spot for pizza lovers in Coconut Grove. This cozy Italian eatery is known for its mouthwatering wood-fired pizzas, fresh ingredients, and welcoming atmosphere.

Bar.Name: Senor Spiky
Bar.Description: Senor Spiky is a popular bar in Coconut Grove known for its eclectic decor, which features a mix of vintage and modern elements, including a mural depicting a spiky-haired character. The bar serves an extensive selection of cocktails, including classic margaritas and mojitos. On weekends, live music performances are held on the outdoor patio area.

Bar.Name: Marina Bar
Bar.Description: A popular spot to relax and enjoy the Miami sunset! Situated on the edge of Dinner Key Marina, this charming bar offers a unique blend of waterfront views and island-inspired cocktails. With its laid-back vibe and friendly staff, the Marina Bar is the perfect place to unwind after a day of exploring the waters of Biscayne Bay.

Bar.Name: Emma's Bar
Bar.Description: Emma's Bar is a popular watering hole located in the heart of Coconut Grove, just a short stroll from Cocowalk. This cozy little dive bar is known for its laid-back atmosphere and wide selection of craft beers, including local favorites from Florida's finest microbreweries.

ClothingShop.Name: Stages
ClothingShop.Description: Stages is a popular clothing boutique that offers a diverse range of styles for both men and women. The store is known for its trendy and affordable clothing, including casual wear, formal attire, and accessories.

ClothingShop.Name: A Rexia Fashions
ClothingShop.Description: This is a small, cozy shop that specializes in women's clothing, accessories, and home decor items. The boutique is known for its unique and eclectic selection of clothing, which includes bohemian-inspired dresses, statement pieces of jewelry, and handmade accessories.

ClothingShop.Name: Burdines
ClothingShop.Description: Burdines is a historic department store located in the heart of downtown Miami. With a rich history dating back to 1895, Burdines is one of the oldest continuously operating businesses in Miami. The iconic store offers a wide range of clothing, shoes, handbags, accessories, and home goods for both men and women.

ClothingShop.Name: Fabio Clothing
ClothingShop.Description: This upscale boutique offers high-quality, stylish clothing for men. The store features an array of designer labels, from casual wear to formal attire, including bespoke suits, dress shirts, dress pants, ties, cufflinks, and more.

ClothingShop.Name: Parade of Shoes
ClothingShop.Description: This store is known for its eclectic and trendy selection of shoes, with everything from stilettos to sneakers. The boutique also carries a variety of clothing items such as dresses, tops, and bottoms to match the perfect outfit. With its colorful and vibrant atmosphere, Parade of Shoes is a must-visit destination for those who want to stand out from the crowd and make a fashion statement.

ClothingShop.Name: Kavix
ClothingShop.Description: Kavix Lingerie is a unique boutique in Coconut Grove that offers a wide array of lingerie from renowned designers. The boutique prides itself on providing an intimate and personalized shopping experience to its discerning clientele. With its exquisite selection of lacy undergarments and elegant loungewear, Kavix Lingerie is an ideal destination for those seeking to elevate their lingerie collection and add a touch of sophistication to their intimate moments.

ClothingShop.Name: The Wild One
ClothingShop.Description: This eclectic shop is known for its wide selection of bohemian-inspired clothing, accessories, and home decor.

ClothingShop.Name: Coco Lynette
ClothingShop.Description: Coco Lynette Fashion is a stylish boutique located in the heart of Coconut Grove at Cocowalk. This enchanting store offers a curated selection of women's clothing and accessories inspired by the vibrant colors and patterns of the Caribbean. From elegant evening gowns to casual streetwear, Coco Lynette Fashion has something for every taste and occasion.

ClothingShop.Name: Rodent in the Grove
ClothingShop.Description: Rodent in the Grove is a family-owned jewelry store located in the heart of Coconut Grove. With a name that may seem unusual at first glance, the store has become a beloved fixture in the community since its opening over 40 years ago. The store's owners are known for their exceptional craftsmanship and unique designs, which often feature tropical motifs inspired by the lush natural surroundings of Coconut Grove. The store offers a wide range of jewelry pieces, from elegant and understated to bold and eye-catching, using high-quality materials such as gold, silver, pearls, and gemstones.
